            "title": "一场文艺复兴的测试",
            "date_published": "2024-10-14T09:12:15.289Z",
            "content_html": "<link rel=\"stylesheet\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-style-marker\" href=\"\\assets\\css\\APlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"\\assets\\js\\APlayer.min.js\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-script-marker\"></script><script class=\"meting-secondary-script-marker\" src=\"\\assets\\js\\Meting.min.js\"></script><img data-src=\"../images/chunking-express.jpg\" alt=\"chunking-express\" style=\"zoom: 10%;\" />\n\n<p>“不知道從什麽時候開始，在每個東西上都有一個日期。秋刀魚會過期，肉醬會過期，連保鮮紙都會過期，我開始懷疑在這個世界上還有什麽東西是不會過期的？”</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h1 id=\"序言\"><a href=\"#序言\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"序言\"></a>序言</h1><p>这是一个对于新的github博客的测试文档。</p>\n<p>由于原先的博客近三年来缺乏维护，导致难以部署，只能使用旧版<code>node.js-12.4.0</code>进行部署，还状况频出，故放弃。</p>\n<p>原博客链接为：<a href=\"https://we1005.junyan.art/\">他的国 (junyan.art)</a></p>\n<p>现采用最新的<code>node.js-20.18.0</code>进行建站，但愿能继续长久维护下去。</p>\n<h2 id=\"引用测试\"><a href=\"#引用测试\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"引用测试\"></a>引用测试</h2><blockquote>\n<p>虞美人·听雨</p>\n<p>【宋】蒋捷</p>\n<p>少年听雨歌楼上，红烛昏罗帐。</p>\n<p>壮年听雨客舟中，江阔云低、断雁叫西风。</p>\n<p>而今听雨僧庐下，鬓已星星也。</p>\n<p>悲欢离合总无情，一任阶前、点滴到天明。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"超链接测试\"><a href=\"#超链接测试\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"超链接测试\"></a>超链接测试</h2><p><a href=\"https://we1005.junyan.art/posts/cfa2b402.html\">当代中国的三大社会思潮 | 他的国 (junyan.art)</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"代码测试\"><a href=\"#代码测试\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码测试\"></a>代码测试</h2><figure class=\"highlight c++\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">double</span>&amp; <span class=\"title\">lala</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">double</span> arg[])</span><span class=\"comment\">//返回一个引用类型</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">double</span>&amp; a = arg[<span class=\"number\">1</span>];</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> a;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">double</span> d_array[<span class=\"number\">3</span>] = &#123; <span class=\"number\">0.00</span>,<span class=\"number\">1.23</span>,<span class=\"number\">3.36</span> &#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">double</span>&amp; qq = <span class=\"built_in\">lala</span>(d_array);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    qq = <span class=\"number\">5.42</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    cout &lt;&lt; d_array[<span class=\"number\">1</span>] &lt;&lt; endl;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"主题自带的功能测试\"><a href=\"#主题自带的功能测试\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"主题自带的功能测试\"></a>主题自带的功能测试</h2><h3 id=\"💥-文本居中引用效果\"><a href=\"#💥-文本居中引用效果\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"💥 文本居中引用效果\"></a>💥 文本居中引用效果</h3><blockquote class=\"blockquote-center\">\n<p>雁门太守行</p>\n<p style=\"font-family: '楷体', 'STKaiti', '华文楷体', 'KaiTi', serif; font-size: 16px;\"> \n    唐·李贺\n</p>\n\n<p>黑云压城城欲摧，甲光向日金鳞开。<br>角声满天秋色里，塞上燕脂凝夜紫。<br>半卷红旗临易水，霜重鼓寒声不起。<br>报君黄金台上意，提携玉龙为君死。</p>\n\n</blockquote>\n\n<h3 id=\"🌟文本高亮\"><a href=\"#🌟文本高亮\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"🌟文本高亮\"></a>🌟文本高亮</h3><p>Lorem <mark class=\"label \">ipsum</mark> <mark class=\"label primary\">dolor sit</mark> amet, consectetur <mark class=\"label success\">adipiscing elit,</mark> sed <mark class=\"label info\">do eiusmod</mark> tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.</p>\n<p>Ut enim <em><mark class=\"label warning\">ad</mark></em> minim veniam, quis <strong><mark class=\"label danger\">nostrud</mark></strong> exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.</p>\n<p>Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate <del><mark class=\"label default\">velit</mark></del> <mark>esse</mark> cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum.</p>\n<div class=\"note default\"><p>default html</p></div>\n\n<h3 id=\"⭐-按钮\"><a href=\"#⭐-按钮\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"⭐ 按钮\"></a>⭐ 按钮</h3><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\">Text</a><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\" title=\"Title\">Text & Title</a>\n\n<div><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\"><i class=\"fa fa-home fa-2x\"></i></a><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\"><i class=\"fa fa-home fa-2x\"></i></a><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\"><i class=\"fa fa-home fa-2x\"></i></a></div>\n<div><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\"><i class=\"fa fa-home fa-lg\"></i></a><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\"><i class=\"fa fa-home fa-lg\"></i></a><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\"><i class=\"fa fa-home fa-lg\"></i></a></div>\n<div><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\"><i class=\"fa fa-home\"></i></a><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\"><i class=\"fa fa-home\"></i></a><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\"><i class=\"fa fa-home\"></i></a></div>\n\n<p><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\"><i class=\"fa fa-home\"></i>Text & Icon (buggy)</a>\n<a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\"><i class=\"fa fa-home fa-fw\"></i>Text & Icon (fixed width)</a></p>\n\n<div class=\"text-center\"><div><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\"><i class=\"fa fa-heading\"></i></a><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\"><i class=\"fab fa-edge\"></i></a><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\"><i class=\"fa fa-times\"></i></a><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\"><i class=\"fa fa-circle-notch\"></i></a></div>\n<div><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\"><i class=\"fa fa-italic\"></i></a><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\"><i class=\"fab fa-scribd\"></i></a></div>\n<div><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\"><i class=\"fab fa-google\"></i></a><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\"><i class=\"fab fa-chrome\"></i></a><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\"><i class=\"fab fa-opera\"></i></a><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\"><i class=\"fa fa-gem fa-rotate-270\"></i></a></div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"text-center\"><a class=\"btn\" href=\"https://github.com\" title=\"GitHub\"><i class=\"fab fa-github fa-fw fa-lg\"></i>GitHub</a></div>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"🐞-自带的友链标签功能\"><a href=\"#🐞-自带的友链标签功能\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"🐞 自带的友链标签功能\"></a>🐞 自带的友链标签功能</h3><div class=\"link-grid\"><div class=\"link-grid-container\">\n<object class=\"link-grid-image\" data=\"/images/apple-touch-icon-next.png\"></object>\n<p>Theme NexT</p><p>Stay Simple. Stay NexT.</p>\n<a href=\"https://theme-next.js.org/\"></a>\n</div><div class=\"link-grid-container\">\n<object class=\"link-grid-image\" data=\"/images/apple-touch-icon-next.png\"></object>\n<p>Theme NexT</p><p>Stay Simple. Stay NexT.</p>\n<a href=\"https://theme-next.js.org/\"></a>\n</div><div class=\"link-grid-container\">\n<object class=\"link-grid-image\" data=\"/images/apple-touch-icon-next.png\"></object>\n<p>Theme NexT</p><p>Stay Simple. Stay NexT.</p>\n<a href=\"https://theme-next.js.org/\"></a>\n</div><div class=\"link-grid-container\">\n<object class=\"link-grid-image\" data=\"/images/apple-touch-icon-next.png\"></object>\n<p>Theme NexT</p><p>Stay Simple. Stay NexT.</p>\n<a href=\"https://theme-next.js.org/\"></a>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"🛠-自带的group-picture功能\"><a href=\"#🛠-自带的group-picture功能\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"🛠 自带的group-picture功能\"></a>🛠 自带的group-picture功能</h3><div class=\"group-picture\"><div class=\"group-picture-row\"><div class=\"group-picture-column\"><img data-src=\"/images/next.svg\"></div><div class=\"group-picture-column\"><img data-src=\"/images/next.svg\"></div><div class=\"group-picture-column\"><img data-src=\"/images/next.svg\"></div></div></div>\n\n<h3 id=\"🌀自带的gallery功能失效\"><a href=\"#🌀自带的gallery功能失效\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"🌀自带的gallery功能失效\"></a>🌀自带的gallery功能失效</h3><p><a href=\"https://theme-next.js.org/docs/advanced-settings/front-matter.html?highlight=gallery#Undocumented-Front-matter-Variables\">https://theme-next.js.org/docs/advanced-settings/front-matter.html?highlight=gallery#Undocumented-Front-matter-Variables</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://localhost:4000/next-gallery/gallery-post.html\">Gallery Post | 他的国</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://localhost:4000/next-gallery/\">next-gallery | 他的国</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"📖自带的note功能\"><a href=\"#📖自带的note功能\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"📖自带的note功能\"></a>📖自带的note功能</h3><div class=\"note info\"><h4 id=\"Info-Header\"><a href=\"#Info-Header\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Info Header\"></a>Info Header</h4><p><strong>Welcome</strong> to <a href=\"https://hexo.io/\">Hexo!</a></p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"note success\"><h4 id=\"Success-Header\"><a href=\"#Success-Header\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Success Header\"></a>Success Header</h4><p><strong>Welcome</strong> to <a href=\"https://hexo.io/\">Hexo!</a></p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"note warning\"><h4 id=\"Warning-Header\"><a href=\"#Warning-Header\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Warning Header\"></a>Warning Header</h4><p><strong>Welcome</strong> to <a href=\"https://hexo.io/\">Hexo!</a></p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"note info no-icon\"><h4 id=\"No-icon-note\"><a href=\"#No-icon-note\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"No icon note\"></a>No icon note</h4><p>Note <strong>without</strong> icon: <code>note info no-icon</code></p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"note danger\"><h4 id=\"Danger-Header\"><a href=\"#Danger-Header\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Danger Header\"></a>Danger Header</h4><p><strong>Welcome</strong> to <a href=\"https://hexo.io/\">Hexo!</a></p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"🌍自定义note\"><a href=\"#🌍自定义note\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"🌍自定义note\"></a>🌍自定义note</h3><p>来自：<a href=\"https://zenreal.github.io/posts/44730/#%E5%81%B4%E6%AC%84%E5%9C%93%E8%A7%92%E5%8C%96\">最新 Hexo NexT v7.4.1 主題優化 | 雲沐居</a></p>\n<p>將以下代碼放<code>source/_data/styles.styl</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">//自定義NOTE</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.alert</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">padding</span>: <span class=\"number\">15px</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">margin-bottom</span>: <span class=\"number\">20px</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">border</span>: <span class=\"number\">1px</span> solid transparent;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">border-radius</span>: <span class=\"number\">4px</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.alert-success</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"number\">#468847</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">background-color</span>: <span class=\"number\">#dff0d8</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">border-color</span>: <span class=\"number\">#d6e9c6</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.alert-info</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"number\">#3a87ad</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">background-color</span>: <span class=\"number\">#e2eaee</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">border-color</span>: <span class=\"number\">#c5d5dd</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.alert-warning</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"number\">#c09853</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">background-color</span>: <span class=\"number\">#fcf8e3</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">border-color</span>: <span class=\"number\">#faebcc</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.alert-danger</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"number\">#b94a48</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">background-color</span>: <span class=\"number\">#f2dede</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">border-color</span>: <span class=\"number\">#ebccd1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<div class=\"alert alert-success\"><i class=\"fa fa-lightbulb-o\"></i> success</div>\n\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\"><i class=\"fa fa-info\"></i> info</div>\n\n<div class=\"alert alert-warning\"><i class=\"fa fa-bell\"></i> warning</div>\n\n<div class=\"alert alert-danger\"><i class=\"fa fa-bug\"></i> danger</div>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span> <span class=\"attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;alert alert-success&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">i</span> <span class=\"attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;fa fa-lightbulb-o&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">i</span>&gt;</span> success<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>🌈<br>🌞<br>🔍<br>这些表情都是哪里来的，为啥默认能显示。<a href=\"https://emojiterra.com/\">🐢 EmojiTerra 🌍 | Emoji Copy &amp; Paste</a></p>\n<p>favicon生成：<a href=\"https://realfavicongenerator.net/\">Favicon Generator for perfect icons on all browsers</a></p>\n<p>👑可以直接copy的</p>\n<img data-src=\"https://img.junyan.art/img/image-20241116195901982.png\" alt=\"image-20241116195901982\" style=\"zoom:50%;\" />\n\n<h3 id=\"✅横向tabs\"><a href=\"#✅横向tabs\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"✅横向tabs\"></a>✅横向tabs</h3><div class=\"tabs\" id=\"sixth-unique-name\"><ul class=\"nav-tabs\"><li class=\"tab active\"><a href=\"#sixth-unique-name-1\"><i class=\"fa fa-text-width\"></i>Solution 1</a></li><li class=\"tab\"><a href=\"#sixth-unique-name-2\"><i class=\"fa fa-font\"></i>Solution 2</a></li><li class=\"tab\"><a href=\"#sixth-unique-name-3\"><i class=\"fa fa-bold\"></i>Solution 3</a></li></ul><div class=\"tab-content\"><div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"sixth-unique-name-1\"><p><strong>This is Tab 1.</strong></p></div><div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"sixth-unique-name-2\"><p><strong>This is Tab 2.</strong></p></div><div class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"sixth-unique-name-3\"><p><strong>This is Tab 3.</strong></p></div></div></div>\n\n<h3 id=\"自定義文字色塊\"><a href=\"#自定義文字色塊\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"自定義文字色塊\"></a>自定義文字色塊</h3><p><a href=\"https://zenreal.github.io/posts/44730/#%E5%81%B4%E6%AC%84%E5%9C%93%E8%A7%92%E5%8C%96\">最新 Hexo NexT v7.4.1 主題優化 | 雲沐居</a></p>\n<p><span id=\"inline-blue\">主題配置文件-蓝</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"inline-purple\">主題配置文件-紫</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"inline-yellow\">主題配置文件-黄</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"inline-green\">主題配置文件-绿</span></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">span</span> <span class=\"attr\">id</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;inline-green&quot;</span>&gt;</span>主題配置文件<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"测试网页自带的字体\"><a href=\"#测试网页自带的字体\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"测试网页自带的字体\"></a>测试网页自带的字体</h3><p>啦啦啦啦啦啦</p>\n<p class=\"kai-ti\">\n  这是使用楷体（KaiTi）字体的段落。\n</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-family: '楷体', 'STKaiti', '华文楷体', 'KaiTi', serif; font-size: 16px;\">   这是使用楷体（KaiTi）字体且大小为16像素的段落。 </p>\n\n<p style=\"font-family: LXGW WenKai Screen, serif; font-size: 16px;\">  \n    它为用户提供了更适合屏幕阅读的字体版本。通过优化字体显示效果和提升兼容性，该项目为用户带来了更加清晰、舒适和一致的阅读体验。这是使用霞鹜文楷字体。 </p>\n\n<p style=\"font-family: serif; font-size: 16px;\">  \n    这是使用serif字体。 </p>\n\n<p style=\"font-family: '宋体',SimSun',serif; font-size: 16px;\">  \n    这是使用宋体。 </p>\n\n<p style=\"font-family: LXGW WenKai Screen, serif;font-size: 22px; color: red; font-weight: bold;\">\n  奇怪，为什么网页默认是18px而不是16px。\n</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"custom-file测试\"><a href=\"#custom-file测试\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"custom_file测试\"></a>custom_file测试</h2><p><a href=\"/customize-header-test/\">自定义文件测试网页</a></p>\n<h1 id=\"古文排版测试\"><a href=\"#古文排版测试\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"古文排版测试\"></a>古文排版测试</h1><p><a href=\"https://sivan.github.io/heti/#example-vertical\">赫蹏 - 一个简约又简单的网页中文排版增强</a></p>\n<style>\n/* 默认情况下隐藏移动消息 */\n.hidden-on-desktop {\n    display: none;\n}\n/* 针对移动设备的媒体查询 */\n@media (max-width: 767px) {\n    /* 在移动设备上隐藏原本的div */\n    .heti--ancient {\n        display: none;\n    }\n    /* 在移动设备上显示消息 */\n    .hidden-on-desktop {\n        display: block;\n        text-align: center; /* 可选：使文本居中 */\n        margin-top: 20px;   /* 可选：添加一些顶部外边距 */\n    }\n}\n</style>\n<div id=\"mobile-message\" class=\"hidden-on-desktop\">请切换到PC端查看</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"heti heti--ancient\">\n  <h2>一剪梅·红藕香残玉簟秋<span class=\"heti-meta heti-small\">[宋]<abbr title=\"号易安居士\">李清照</abbr></span></h2>\n  <p class=\"heti-verse heti-x-large\">\n    红藕香残玉簟秋。轻解罗裳，独上兰舟<span class=\"heti-hang\">。</span><br>\n    云中谁寄锦书来，雁字回时，月满西楼<span class=\"heti-hang\">。</span><br>\n    花自飘零水自流。一种相思，两处闲愁<span class=\"heti-hang\">。</span><br>\n    此情无计可消除，才下眉头，却上心头<span class=\"heti-hang\">。</span>\n  </p>\n</div>\n</br>\n</br>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"heti--vertical heti--ancient\">\n              <h1>出師表</h1>\n              <p class=\"heti-small\">作者：<abbr title=\"字孔明\">諸葛亮</abbr>（<heti-spacing class=\"heti-spacing-start\">181</heti-spacing>年－<heti-spacing class=\"heti-spacing-start\">234</heti-spacing>年<heti-spacing class=\"heti-spacing-start heti-spacing-end\">10</heti-spacing>月<heti-spacing class=\"heti-spacing-start heti-spacing-end\">8</heti-spacing>日）</p>\n              <p>先帝創業未半，而中道崩殂；今天下三分，益州疲弊，此誠危急存亡之秋也﹗然侍衞之臣，不懈於內；忠志之士，忘身於外者，蓋追先帝之殊遇，欲報之於陛下也。</p>\n              <p>誠宜開張聖聽，以光先帝遺德，恢弘志士之氣﹔不宜妄自菲薄，引喻失義，以塞忠諫之路也。</p>\n              <p>宮中、府中，俱為一體；陟罰臧否，不宜異同。若有作姦、犯科，及為忠善者，宜付有司，論其刑賞，以昭陛下平明之治；不宜偏私，使內外異法也。</p>\n              <p>侍中、侍郎郭攸之、費禕、董允等，此皆良實，志慮忠純，是以先帝簡拔以遺陛下。愚以為宮中之事，事無大小，悉以咨之，然後施行，必能裨補闕漏，有所廣益。將軍向寵，性行淑均，曉暢軍事，試用於昔日，先帝稱之曰「能<heti-adjacent class=\"heti-adjacent-half\">」</heti-adjacent>，是以眾議舉寵為督。愚以為營中之事，悉以咨之，必能使行陣和睦，優劣得所。</p>\n              <p>親賢臣，遠小人，此先漢所以興隆也﹔親小人，遠賢臣，此後漢所以傾頹也。先帝在時，每與臣論此事，未嘗不歎息痛恨於桓、靈也！侍中、尚書、長史、參軍，此悉貞良死節之臣，願陛下親之、信之，則漢室之隆，可計日而待也。</p>\n            </div>\n\n\n<h1 id=\"自定义html代码测试\"><a href=\"#自定义html代码测试\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"自定义html代码测试\"></a>自定义html代码测试</h1><h3 id=\"歌单\"><a href=\"#歌单\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"歌单\"></a>歌单</h3><iframe frameborder=\"no\" border=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" width=330 height=450 src=\"//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=0&id=12748367586&auto=0&height=430\"></iframe>\n\n<h3 id=\"切换字体按钮\"><a href=\"#切换字体按钮\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"切换字体按钮\"></a>切换字体按钮</h3><style> \n.gear-container {\n    position: fixed;\n    top: 450px;\n    right: 20px;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    align-items: flex-end;\n}\n.gear-button {\n    background-color: #0D8BCD;\n    color: white;\n    border: none;\n    border-radius: 10px;\n    padding: 10px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    font-size: 16px;\n}\n.submenu {\n    display: none;\n    position: absolute;\n    bottom: 50px;\n    right: 20px;\n    background-color: #0D8BCD;\n    border: none;\n    border-radius: 10px;\n    box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n    z-index: 1000;\n}\n.submenu-button {\n    width: 100px;\n    padding: 10px;\n    border: none;\n    border-radius: 10px;\n    background-color: #0D8BCD;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    color: #FFFFFF;\n}\n.submenu-button:hover {\n    background-color: #e0e0e0;\n}\n.submenu.active {\n    display: block;\n}\n</style>\n<div class=\"gear-container\">\n  <button id=\"gear-button\" class=\"gear-button\">⚙️</button>\n  <div id=\"submenu\" class=\"submenu\">\n  </div>\n</div>\n<script>\n  var submenuElement = document.getElementById('submenu');\n  var links = [\n  { text: '楷体', fontFamily: 'KaiTi' }, // 添加 fontFamily 属性来指定字体\n  { text: '鹭霞文楷', fontFamily: 'LXGW WenKai Screen' }, // 示例字体，你可以根据需要更改\n  { text: 'Courier New', fontFamily: 'Courier New' }, // 示例字体，你可以根据需要更改\n  { text: '原始字体', fontFamily: 'Noto Serif SC' },\n  { text: '宋体', fontFamily: '宋体' }\n];\n// 创建一个函数来更改字体\nfunction changeFont(fontFamily) {\n  document.body.style.fontFamily = fontFamily;\n    // 选择所有具有 .post-body 类的元素，并更改它们的字体家族\n  var postBodies = document.getElementsByClassName('post-body');\n  for (var i = 0; i < postBodies.length; i++) {\n    postBodies[i].style.fontFamily = fontFamily;\n  }\n}\n links.forEach(function(link) {\n  var a = document.createElement('button');\n  a.textContent = link.text;\n  a.className = 'submenu-button'; \n  a.onclick = function(event) {\n  changeFont(link.fontFamily); // 调用 changeFont 函数，并传入字体名称\n  };\n  submenuElement.appendChild(a);\n  });\n  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', (event) => {\n    const gearButton = document.getElementById('gear-button');\n    const submenu = document.getElementById('submenu');\n    gearButton.addEventListener('click', () => {\n      submenu.classList.toggle('active');\n    });\n    // Optionally, close the submenu if a click is detected outside of it\n    document.addEventListener('click', (event) => {\n      if (!submenu.contains(event.target) && event.target !== gearButton) {\n        submenu.classList.remove('active');\n      }\n    });\n  });\n</script>\n\n",
